headline: How Marriott Is Sharpening Luxury Strategy and Gearing Up for W Hotel Debut in Saudi Arabia
summary: Marriott International's Luxury Group, which encompasses The Ritz-Carlton, Bulgari Hotels & Resorts, St. Regis Hotels & Resorts, Edition and more, said it is working on experiences that "resonate deeply."
